{"tid":464020,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"新《流星花園》出爐 ！","createTime":"2017-11-10T05:58:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-11T07:31:54.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"c8ef9d453eee165a2c95a61fddcfcca795f01a26","tid":464020,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T05:58:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171110/large/1510283102_67cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171110%2Flarge%2F1510283102_67cc.jpg&h=41c21df8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左起： 「道明寺」王鶴棣、「美作」梁靖康、 「花澤類」官鴻同 「西門」吳希澤。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171110/large/1510283108_689d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171110%2Flarge%2F1510283108_689d.jpg&h=672fe2a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「杉菜」沈月<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171110/large/1510283104_b5b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171110%2Flarge%2F1510283104_b5b1.jpg&h=2dcd5c46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無綫劇集成日重拍，台灣大陸又何嘗唔係。相隔16年（16年！）《流星花園》又重拍。仍然係金牌製作人柴智屏操刀，之前網上已流傳所謂「新F4」，分別係：<br />\n<br />\n王鶴棣飾道明寺<br />\n官鴻飾花澤類<br />\n梁靖康飾美作<br />\n吳希澤飾西門<br />\n杉菜&mdash;&mdash;大陸女星沈月<br />\n<br />\n所謂「新F4」平均身高185cm，一字排開好似屏風樓。四子平均年齡21歲。名字好陌生？因為係強國版。至於有冇「毀童年」嘅感覺呢&hellip;&hellip;唔睇咪冇囉。22歲嘅官鴻係台灣人，19歲嘅王鶴棣來自成都、23歲嘅梁靖康來自廣州、21歲嘅吳希澤來自深圳。四人都係經公開甄選，方法係喺台北、香港、新加坡、洛杉磯同大陸嘅大學搵，劇組聲稱收到超過30,000份履歷。<br />\n<br />\n已為人母嘅大S徐熙媛接受傳媒訪問時當然大讚「新F4條件真的很棒」，咁佢會否喺新版演出一角呢？佢話：「內容會有很多彩蛋，我就不多說啦！」仔仔周渝民對於「接班人選」則回應：「好美呀！」<br />\n<br />\n2017《流星花園》出年暑假上，到時四人仲會舉行全球演唱會，四男一女全新卡士噚日喺上海晒冷，四位男主角同之前猜測嘅一樣，係女主角沈月先至係surprise。大陸網媒紛紛引述呢句網民留言「誰演杉菜肯定是拯救了銀河系的女孩」，咁沈月（呀，唔記得講，唔係邱淑貞個女嗰個沈月）有冇大S徐熙媛殺傷力咁大呢？嗯&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n沈月話，今次搵佢演杉菜壓力特別大，當得知自己中選嗰陣，佢話佢「就穿著睡衣在樓下跑了兩圈」，又話好多女仔都會喺杉菜身上見到自己嘅影子：「我覺得杉菜就是20歲時候平凡又不普通的女孩子。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/realtime/article/20171110/57440742\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171110%2F57440742&d=YRk44BQFTIteAawND%2FDYk26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=006b5bfc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171110%2F57440742&h=5ce45760\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/realtime/article/20171110/57440742</a>"},{"pid":"f13a626fd741dbf8b70d153da0c06b79fbed4a44","tid":464020,"uid":69741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T06:03:49.000Z","msg":"唔係見到簡體字仲以為韓國翻拍"},{"pid":"58b1abfabbbfb067b046580cc71e2138920201bb","tid":464020,"uid":49151,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T06:07:32.000Z","msg":"好撚mk，仲有4個個樣差唔多嘅"},{"pid":"c109a49d9f01711893dae32f3b100c80a0a93574","tid":464020,"uid":49664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:21:44.000Z","msg":"估中花澤  官鴻"},{"pid":"1bb957761cf4434b3b0d126ba3a26692f6a80e25","tid":464020,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:24:45.000Z","msg":"嚇死人咩 <br />\n沈月飾杉菜"},{"pid":"286eed37d1e4fcab471cd5b7ca6c6b231db280cf","tid":464020,"uid":49664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:31:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>嚇死人咩 <br />\n沈月飾杉菜</blockquote><br />\n邱淑貞大女  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c96c35c9ab8b764633d62ab95589bf58acf90df4","tid":464020,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:38:04.000Z","msg":"點解依版美作西門靚仔過道明寺花澤類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"357621829c839c3dd0f61f09a36c92a